{"type":null,"faqId":17173,"title":"荣耀畅玩手环(AF500)_手机黑屏休眠后，手环也会跟手机连接断开，这是怎么回事？","answer":"<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">这是设置问题。</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">1. 点击设置-&gt;省电管理，在受保护的后台应用选择手环应用。</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">2. 点击设置-&gt;权限管理-&gt;应用程序，选择手环应用，勾选信任此应用程序。</p>\n<br>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\"></p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9815","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1418204436000,"seriesProductName":"AF500","visitedTimes":147,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀，畅玩，手环，AF500，黑屏，休眠，连接，断开","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}